cing activities he joined perseus llc in may  he served as a managing director of nassau capital llc where he was responsible for all aspects of the direct investment process including identifying and developing opportunities negotiating and closing transactions and developing strategic plans and exit strategies for portfolio companies prior to that mr glovier served as an associate at goldman sachs and co in the mergers and acquisitions structured finance and leveraged buyout groups from  to  and  to  he served as a management consultant of the boston consulting group inc he has been independent director of hrg group inc since january  he served as the chairman of the board of directors at maritime telecommunications network inc he has been a director of opus bank since september  mr glovier received a ba cum laude from princeton university an mec with high distinction from james cook university in australia and an mba as a palmer scholar from the wharton school of the university of pennsylvaniaread full background corporate headquarters  market streetsan francisco california united statesphone fax  board members memberships directorpi encorp llcdirectorconverse incdirectoropex corporationchairman and chief executive officerpensco trust companypresentdirectoropus bankpresentindependent directorhrg group inc education ba princeton universitymba university of pennsylvania  the wharton schoolme james cook university other affiliations nassau capital llcperseus llcpi encorp llcthe boston consulting group inchrg group incfortress investment group llcconverse incgoldman sachs  co llcopex corporationprinceton universitynew york power authorityopus bankuniversity of pennsylvania  the wharton schooljames cook university annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation there is no total compensation data available request profile update   the information and data displayed in this pr