ne  mr glovier worked at goldman sachs  co in the mergers  acquisitions structured finance and leveraged buyout groups and was also a management consultant at the boston consulting group he has served as a director of companies in the financial services business services branded consumer products intellectual property pharmaceutical alternative energy communications and manufacturing areas and as chairman of the board of maritime telecommunications network mr glovier holds a ba from princeton university a mec from james cook university in australia and an mba as a palmer scholar from the wharton school at the university of pennsylvania mr glover is a member of the directors loan committee mr gloviers qualifications to serve on our board of directors include his experience as a managing director for fortress with responsibilities for the management of the origination execution and monitoring of private equity mezzanine and other investments and his service on the investment committee of a number of fortress investment funds which invest in mortgagebacked securities loans and other creditrelated opportunities source opus bank on    sign up for equilar atlas and view curtis a gloviers full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like curtis a glovier more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in curtis a gloviers network and community follow changes in curtis a gloviers employment and moneyinmotion connect with curtis a glovier through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example curtis a glovier curtis a gloviers connections  sign up now to view curtis a gloviers  connections » gerald luterman lead independent director hrg group inc frank ianna board member hrg group inc michael l allison former executive vice president and chief credit officer cascade bancorp omar m asali former president chief executive officer and direc